What's new in version 0.5.1 Beta?

- Added baobab boards
- Added a stage and a plate of baobab
- Added vanilla recipes from baobab boards
- Added Scorpion
- Be careful scorpio gives a nausea effect for 40 seconds
- Scorpions appear in the desert
- Quicksand can no longer be destroyed, as it is an extremely loose substance
- A bucket of quicksand is only the subject of creativity
- A bottle of water makes a quicksand into normal sand
